                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="service-content-inner d-flex align-items-center bg-white border border-primary rounded p-4 ps-0">
                            <div class="service-icon p-4">
                                <i class="fa fa-globe fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service-content">
                                <h5 class="mb-4">Personalized Wellness Programs</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    We believe in offering personalized wellness programs tailored to the individual needs of our guests. Our experienced therapists and wellness experts work with you to create a customized spa experience 
                                    that addresses your specific concerns and goals
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="service-content-inner d-flex align-items-center bg-white border border-primary rounded p-4 ps-0">
                            <div class="service-icon p-4">
                                <i class="fa fa-hotel fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service-content">
                                <h5 class="mb-4">Complementary Wellness Amenitiess</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    In addition to our spa treatments, we offer a range of complementary wellness amenities designed to enhance your overall experience. Our state-of-the-art fitness center, complete with modern equipment and personal trainers, 
                                    allows you to maintain your fitness routine while traveling
                                </p>
                            </div>
